name: Effect of chapter on department of health
text: §149A-4  Effect of chapter on department of health.  Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to amend or alter the functions, duties, and powers of the department of health relative to chapters 321, 322, 328, and 330. [L 1972, c 58, pt of §1; am L 1975, c 126, pt of §1]
